# Demo recording for the README. Render with Charm VHS (https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs):
#   vhs demo.tape   ->   demo.gif
Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 640
Set Padding 18
Set Theme "Dracula"

Type "npx ctxdiet"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "npx ctxdiet fix"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "y"
Enter
Sleep 5s
